<h1>Sign up for a Department tour!</h1>
<p>
  HKN provides tours of the Berkeley EECS department.
  Sign up here, and your request will be sent to the HKN officer corps.
  If you have any special requests, list them in the additional comments section.
</p>

<p>
  Tours are offered for only the following Dates and Times:
</p>

<ul>
  <li>Thursday at 6 PM Pacific Time,</li>
  <li>Saturday at 10 AM Pacific Time, and</li>
  <li>Saturday at 12 PM Pacific Time</li>
</ul>

<p>
  In the "Additional Comments" section, please provide the following information:
</p>

<ul>
  <li> Tour Emphasis (Select any):
     <ul>
        <li>Getting to know the department physically</li>
        <li>Personal Experience</li>
        <li>Educational recommendations (classes, workload, academic emphasis, research, etc)</li>
        <li>General recommendations (living, commute, social life, clubs, community)</li>
        <li>Hearing about faculty</li>
        <li>Getting to know other prospective students and maybe some more</li>
     </ul>
   <li>Tell us a bit about yourself - Where you from, academic status (HS Student, CC students, other), are you planning to apply to Cal/already applied/got accepted/other, etc.</li>
   <li>Number of Tour Guests - Do you plan on bringing guests to the tour? Parents are welcome and encouraged to join, you can also bring a friend with you!</li>
</ul>

<p>
  Please allow three days for confirmation.
</p>


<p>
    Note: Tour requests made less than 48 hours in advance from the requested time cannot be guaranteed.
</p>

  <% if @errors && @errors.any? %>
    <div id="errorExplanation">
      <h2>There are <%= pluralize(@errors.count, "error") %> with the information entered:</h2>
      <ul>
      <% @errors.each_pair do |field, msg| %>
        <li><%= msg %></li>
      <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>
  <%- end -%>

<%= form_tag(dept_tour_signup_path, method: :post) do%>
  <div class="field">
    <%= label_tag :name, "Name", class: 'required-field' %>
    <%= text_field_tag :name, params[:name] %>
  </div>

  <div class="field">
    <%= label_tag :date, "Desired date & time", class: 'required-field' %>
    <%= text_field_tag :date, params[:date], class: "datetimepicker depttourpicker" %>
  </div>

  <div class="field">
    <%= label_tag :email, "Contact email address", class: 'required-field' %>
    <%= text_field_tag :email, params[:email] %>
  </div>

  <div class="field">
    <%= label_tag :email_confirmation, "Re-type email", class: 'required-field' %>
    <%= text_field_tag :email_confirmation, params[:email_confirmation] %>
  </div>

  <div class="field">
    <%= label_tag :phone, "Contact phone number", class: 'required-field' %>
    <%= text_field_tag :phone, params[:phone] %>
  </div>

  <div class="field">
    <%= label_tag :comments, "Additional comments:" %>
    <%= text_area_tag :comments, params[:comments] %>
  </div>

  <div class="field">
    <br />
    <%= captcha %>
  </div>

  <div class="field-submit">
    <%= submit_tag "Submit" %>
  </div>

  <div>
    <p><span class="required-field"></span> denotes a required field</p>
  </div>
<% end %>
